@startuml component_us086_client_server
title US086 — Client-Server Architecture

skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 12

component "Pilot Client App" <<client>> as Client

component "Main Application Server" <<server>> as Server {
  component "TCP Server\nDaemon" as ServerDaemon
  component "PilotClientHandler" as Handler
  component "RemotePilotService" as Service
  component "FCO Controllers" as Controllers {
    component US072
    component US080
    component US085
    component US111
    component US112
    component US121
  }
  component "Database" as DB
}

component "Remote Accesses\nLogging Server" <<udp_server>> as Logger

Client --> ServerDaemon : TCP connect (Pilot port)
ServerDaemon --> Handler : spawn per\nconnection
Handler --> Service : calls
Service --> Controllers : delegates
Controllers --> DB : JPA
Handler --> Logger : UDP datagram

note right of Handler
  Protocol: text-based
  AUTH|user|pass
  CREATE_FLIGHT_PLAN|...
  LIST_FLEET
  VALIDATE_FLIGHT_PLAN|...
  GENERATE_REPORT|...
  MONTHLY_REPORT|...
  QUIT
end note

note left of Client
  Standalone Java console app
  No direct DB access
  TCP only
end note
@enduml
